The paper discusses the visualization of AutoAI's model generation process, which involves both human-computer interaction (HCI) and machine learning (LG) techniques. The paper also mentions the use of artificial intelligence (AI) and information retrieval (IR) in AutoAI systems. Finally, the paper aims to increase trust in AutoAI systems, which is a topic related to social impact (SI) in computer science.
